title: TutsPlus - Mastering Animal Anatomy in Digital Painting
description: Concept artists need to have a solid understanding of animal anatomy, including all different kinds of animals, like mammals, birds, reptiles, fish and insects. Learning animal anatomy can make it a lot easier to come up with good concepts in games, movies and other entertainment industries. So in this course, digital artist Char Reed will take you through the process of digitally painting animal anatomy
